Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在找誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面就交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就到那條河裡去洗洗眼睛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:02:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的能力 暗殺專家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單靠鋒利的爪子\N和敏銳的嗅覺是贏不了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.75,0:02:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直與你走到今天 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何時何地都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這一次只能認輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的細胞在你體內自由地來回游動 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以製造出專屬你的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正處於融合狀態 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共享這個肉體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共享
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.11,0:02:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有惟獨我能做到的殘忍殺人手法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢奪走屬於你的細胞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然自殺 這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同歸於盡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不出所料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是身體共享嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.27,0:04:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛入對方的身體中就不會受到攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.75,0:04:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是這個忍術的最大優點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止還沒人這麼幹過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吧 是時候來個痛快了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 你小子快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失血過多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔下狗獨自逃命了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個正確的判斷 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子比我還無情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:07:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤丸 你真的很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧你拖延了敵人很長時間 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方也負傷不輕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就夠了 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經幹得很不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的名字叫赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天開始由你照顧它了 行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是牙 多多關照啊 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是敗給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.35,0:08:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接得好 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 幹得漂亮 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我認真點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼天真
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 牙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是你 你和赤丸要一起變強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和赤丸一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.15,0:09:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 赤丸 就這樣 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中動態追蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來旋轉三次 瞄準目標
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也會一直在一起 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面就由我來保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子 設陷阱算計我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:11:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左近 你在哪裡 左近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.65,0:11:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左近 左近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真夠煩的啊 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫那麼大聲 震得我眼睛疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我想現在就宰了他 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻到了睡覺的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我生擒那些混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我醒了親手處置他們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要生擒他們啊 左近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手的時候我們兩個一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果冒然進攻就會被躲開 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.31,0:12:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成自相殘殺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.55,0:12:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著吧  柳之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的血繼限界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身放出骨頭來攻擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把自己的骨頭拔出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用骨頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當刀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這並非尋常的骨頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最高密度的骨頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛如鋼鐵般堅韌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種骨頭 由我來折斷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有五種舞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為你已經摸清我的實力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就特別讓你見識一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椿之舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我打扁你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在一步步地向這邊靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 是血跡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 雖說救回了赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好像太過勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這氣味 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼那些傢伙也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 一定要盡快離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為疼痛與失血 意識開始模糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體完全動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子只留下了上衣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:19:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃到河裡去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被趕進死胡同了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以準確的時機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓三人分開攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做過不少練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當複雜的曲子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但立刻發現是用笛子操縱這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能聽懂曲子的複雜 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子挺有兩下的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你無法徹底瞭解這首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 藝術與我無緣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 既然是用笛子操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就表示曲子中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.74,0:20:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有操縱每個人行動的音節組合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.10,0:20:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說我對自己的分析能力充滿自信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可這一次真的麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我根本就不懂樂譜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽過這曲子的傢伙沒有一個能活著的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終曲第九節
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔境之亂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲調變了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.85,0:22:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用通靈術同時操縱三具靈獸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.65,0:22:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無破綻的攻防
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.35,0:22:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不甘心 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.91,0:22:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好那傢伙也是將棋高手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.85,0:22:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我的忍具也所剩無幾了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.15,0:22:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 還想大幹一場呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.65,0:22:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 該行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.35,0:22:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭也好笑也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.05,0:22:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能放手一搏了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.65,0:22:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.61,0:23:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛招 男子漢鹿丸 起死回生的賭注
